# QA Rules

When relevant, verify with:

```powershell
uv run ruff check src/backend src/mcp-server
uv run pytest -q
cd src/frontend; npm ci; npm run lint; npm test; npm run build
```

First-time frontend setup (no CI intent): `npm install` in `src/frontend`. CI-equivalent checks use `npm ci` when `package-lock.json` is present.